{"tid":1702520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"領展cctv疑似影到周同學跌落黎嘅一刻以及相關嘅假設，分析和跟進","createTime":"2019-11-09T17:22:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T08:04:19.000Z","uid":303090,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"9c0d27244b9804b9e8230169cbde097025f71452","tid":1702520,"uid":303090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:22:30.000Z","msg":"首先，係呢度同周同學做個祝福<br />\n希望佢沉冤得雪，早日安心上路<br />\n<br />\n入正題<br />\n<br />\nCCTV：跌落嚟嘅一刻<br />\n<br />\nC30 010224<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gyBUg7t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgyBUg7t.jpg&h=050f922c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n車上面果兩條嘢平時swing唔會有架<br />\n係010223-010224之間肉色嘢係車頂閃現，然後冇咗<br />\n<br />\nC30 010700<br />\n消防係呢個位除頭盔<br />\n應該可以確定周同學嘅墮下位置係呢度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/my1AL2S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmy1AL2S.jpg&h=945a7add&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啱啱路過廣明苑一棟樓嘅時侯，睇到呢支cam<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BpAehgo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBpAehgo.jpg&h=3621201b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有機會睇到事發一刻<br />\n亦係希望可以公開<br />\n<br />\n所以上面個肉色影係咪真。跌落黎嘅一瞬呢？<br />\n<br />\n如果係嘅話，衍生出以下問題<br />\n（大膽假設）：<br />\n<br />\n1 係領展CCTV C31 嘅 010217<br />\n出現咗周同學嘅最後一個身影<br />\n短短7秒就&ldquo;跌&rdquo;咗落去？<br />\n真係有人推嘅話，人從何來？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知大家有冇留意隔離有條後樓梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有人係010217由後樓梯突然衝出<br />\n係周同學嘅頭度狠狠敲一棍，然後氹佢落樓<br />\n係偷襲嘅話絕對有機會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知大家又有冇留意條樓梯去度邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢上通尚德平台，落一層就係周同學被消防發現嘅一層，根本上係呢個3樓右半層cctv真空咗嘅情況下，咩都有可能發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尚德平台：<br />\n因為上咗平台，邊度都去到<br />\n所以犯人有機會會上去<br />\n下面係我個人認為有需要公開嘅CCTV<br />\n有機會follow up到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/orqqoUP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2ForqqoUP.jpg&h=9813ae62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gTFBvAx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgTFBvAx.jpg&h=69ec1656&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，都有避晒cctv嘅路走到<br />\n不過點都要睇下先<br />\n<br />\n2樓：<br />\n唔知大家又有冇發現周同學墮樓處嘅旁邊<br />\n其實係條好長嘅斜路走上同落嘅<br />\n而當日狗狗嘅部署就係果度附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要meet up返佢哋話都冇咁易<br />\n<br />\n條樓梯仲可以落其他層，不過我覺得係上下果層走嘅機會最大，其他師兄可以去睇睇，幫我補充下<br />\n<br />\n但要補充一點：<br />\n如果係熟路或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有組織</span></strong>嘅話根本可以係現場避過所有CCTV<br />\n<br />\n2<br />\n 2，3樓嘅CCTV真空期<br />\n啱啱去現場觀察過啲cctv<br />\n發現要等到有右半層真空<br />\n兩支cam射晒同一面嘅時侯<br />\n真係唔係咁容易撞到<br />\n仲要咁啱死咗人，但係乜都影唔倒？！<br />\n可能咩？除非係有組織，有計劃嘅行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">陰謀論</span></span><br />\n呢個會唔會係中共<span style=\"color: red;\">煽</span>動民憤<br />\n借機出軍&ldquo;平亂&rdquo;嘅引線？<br />\n<br />\n無論點都好<br />\n希望大家可以睇睇佢<br />\n幫周同學做最後一件我哋可以做嘅事"},{"pid":"ff4bda1412363595c77ce2a3a8ad163f5e69253e","tid":1702520,"uid":303090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:23:39.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b348c24408982de7ce0aee3a8014ae5f3236fa","tid":1702520,"uid":303090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:24:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6077c40fc3a62fb9281d2c088688dc8184e7257","tid":1702520,"uid":303090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:24:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1887b07d6ad9da8c4722f983079c47b14f9442b","tid":1702520,"uid":303090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:25:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd11d304cc5bd71989f3e88985ea836e4f688cfc","tid":1702520,"uid":303090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:27:18.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"732e60708dfc8e1ab2e68217dbbf93ba6fad0ed5","tid":1702520,"uid":242978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:28:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"81ebcb45b777804cfedf89d4714f279f97e3ea00","tid":1702520,"uid":303090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:28:41.000Z","msg":"幫我推下同睇下plz"},{"pid":"f8457b39928939ff2410d3dd5fbdaf6dca218326","tid":1702520,"uid":242978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbaa3ebbb3851e82870fa607ddb934e233fdfb3a","tid":1702520,"uid":303090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推下"},{"pid":"2a3beb8658f4ac25734c2a367f268c246a2af199","tid":1702520,"uid":89923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:29:48.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"6a95d2b69a98877b9c39db40c7ac87f2657cae18","tid":1702520,"uid":303090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:29:59.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733e542cae02f08b503e620c4cd5b3042d295bc1","tid":1702520,"uid":303090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:30:39.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"ab07a7ca50327c4800bc27fc3efa46e86d870f21","tid":1702520,"uid":303090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:31:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/as